# Load order matters: fzf-tab must come before zsh-autosuggestions and
# zsh-syntax-highlighting so it can hook into the completion system before
# they wrap zle widgets.
#
# zsh-syntax-highlighting is skipped on Linux because its self-insert /
# bracketed-paste widget wrapping causes doubled input on Linux SSH terminals
# (typing "ls" produces "lssls"). macOS terminals don't trigger this.
